# Rust Conventions

## Error Handling
```rust
#[derive(Debug, thiserror::Error)]
pub enum AppError {
    #[error("not found: {0}")]
    NotFound(String),
    #[error("database error: {0}")]
    Database(#[from] sqlx::Error),
}
```
- Never `unwrap()` in production: use `?`

## Async: Tokio
```rust
#[tokio::main]
async fn main() -> anyhow::Result<()> { ... }
```

## Ownership
- Prefer borrowing (`&T`) over cloning
- `Arc<T>` for shared state across threads
